    "corr = data['Distance from the airport'].corr(data['Price'])\n",
    "print('Correlation Coefficient:', corr)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Plot a scatter plot\n",
    "plt.scatter(data['Distance from the airport'], data['Price'])\n",
    "plt.xlabel('Variable 1')\n",
    "plt.ylabel('Variable 2')\n",
    "plt.title('Scatter Plot of Variable 1 vs Variable 2')\n",
    "plt.show()\n",
    "\n",
    "# Plot a line of best fit\n",
    "plt.scatter(data['Distance from the airport'], data['Price'])\n",
    "plt.xlabel('Variable 1')\n",
    "plt.ylabel('Variable 2')\n",
    "plt.title('Scatter Plot of Variable 1 vs Variable 2')\n",
    "z = np.polyfit(data['Distance from the airport'], data['Price'], 1)\n",
    "p = np.poly1d(z)\n",
    "plt.plot(data['Distance from the airport'], p(data['Distance from the airport']), \"r--\")\n",
    "plt.show()\n",
    "\n",
    "# Plot a heatmap\n",
    "plt.hist2d(data['Distance from the airport'], data['Price'], bins=(20, 20), cmap=plt.cm.jet)\n",
    "plt.xlabel('Variable 1')\n",
    "plt.ylabel('Variable 2')\n",
    "plt.title('Heatmap of Variable 1 vs Variable 2')\n",
    "plt.colorbar()\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]

    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "\n",
    "# Load the data into a Pandas DataFrame\n",
    "data = pd.read_csv('House Price India.csv')\n",
    "\n",
    "# Calculate basic descriptive statistics\n",
    "mean = np.mean(data['Price'])\n",
    "median = np.median(data['Price'])\n",
    "mode = data['Price'].mode()[0]\n",
    "std_dev = np.std(data['Price'])\n",
    "min_val = np.min(data['Price'])\n",
    "max_val = np.max(data['Price'])\n",
    "\n",
    "# Print the results\n",
    "print('Mean:', mean)\n",
    "print('Median:', median)\n",
    "print('Mode:', mode)\n",
    "print('Standard Deviation:', std_dev)\n",
    "print('Minimum Value:', min_val)\n",
    "print('Maximum Value:', max_val)\n",
    "\n",
    "# Plot a histogram\n",
    "plt.hist(data['Price'], bins=20)\n",
    "plt.xlabel('Price')\n",
    "plt.ylabel('Frequency')\n",
    "plt.title('Histogram of Price')\n",
    "plt.show()\n",
    "\n",
    "# Plot a box plot\n",
    "plt.boxplot(data['Price'])\n",
    "plt.xlabel('Price')\n",
    "plt.title('Box Plot of Price')\n",
    "plt.show()\n",
    "\n",
    "# Plot a density plot\n",
    "data['Price'].plot.kde()\n",
    "plt.xlabel('Price')\n",
    "plt.title('Density Plot of Price')\n",
    "plt.show()\n"
   ]
  },
